Plot: Fred Z. Randall is geeky and obnoxious spacecraft designer, who gets the chance to make his dream come true and travel to Mars as a member of the first manned flight there.
Title: RocketMan
Writer: Oren Aviv (story), Craig Mazin (story), Greg Erb (story), Craig Mazin (screenplay), Greg Erb (screenplay)
Actors: Harland Williams, Jessica Lundy, William Sadler, Jeffrey DeMunn
